IRS990EZ.PrimaryExemptPurposeTxt: WELFARE AND SUPPORT OF HISPANIC STUDENTS AT UNIVERSITY OF HOUSTON.

ProgramSrvcAccomplishmentGrp.DescriptionProgramSrvcAccomTxt: HBSA HAD PREPARED A MULTITUDE OF EVENTS, MOST BEING VIRTUAL, FOR MEMBERS TO CONTINUE TO ADVANCE IN THEIR INVOLVEMENT AND ALSO IMPROVE THEMSELVES PERSONALLY, AND PROFESSIONALLY. OUR 5 PILLARS: FAMILIA, LEADERSHIP, ACADEMICS, PROFESSIONALISM, AND SERVICE, CONTINUED TO BE EMPHASIZED AND CARRIED OUT. WITH THE CONTINUED IMPROVEMENT OF ADJUSTING TO A VIRTUAL ENVIRONMENT, HBSA WAS ABLE TO BE AWARDED THE BAUER COLLEGE OF BUSINESS BEST STUDENT ORGANIZATION OF THE YEAR FOR 2021. THIS IS A MAJOR ACHIEVEMENT DUE TO HOW MANY GOOD STUDENT ORGANIZATIONS THERE ARE AT BAUER, AND SHOWS HOW PREPARED AND ORGANIZED HBSA IS.
